# MoneyRate Bot  

This bot is designed to convert currency rates in Telegram.  

## Technologies Used:  
- Python  
- Telegram API  
- python-telegram-bot  

## How to Use:  
1. Run the `main.py` file to start the bot.  
2. Use the Telegram bot to check exchange rates.  
3. Enter the amount and currency code to convert (e.g., `15000 RUB UZS`).  

## Features:  
✅ Converts between USD, EUR, RUB, and UZS  
✅ Provides real-time exchange rates  
✅ Simple and easy-to-use interface  

## Installation:  
```sh
git clone https://github.com/YourUsername/moneyrate-bot.git  
cd moneyrate-bot  
pip install -r requirements.txt  
python main.py
